## AI Enhanced Components Notice

This strategyai repository includes AI-powered components:

- `ai_generator.py` - AI strategy code generation
- `backtester.py` - Historical backtesting engine
- `api/index.py` - Serverless API with validation

**These AI components are subject to additional licensing terms:**

